casebody.data:
M. A. Galbreath, Plaintiff in Error, v. J. Lee McCory, as County Judge of Volusia County, and Others, Defendants in Error. Tom B. Stewart and R. P. Hamlin, for Plaintiff in Error; Landis, Fish & Hull, for Defendants in Error.

A Writ of Error to the Circuit Court for Volusia County.

Writ of Error dismissed by the Court as presenting a moot question.
